member.summary:
Initializes a new instance of the 
class as specified by , 
and ".

member.remarks:
Express this value as a string of the form <search-state>;<results-condition>;<http-method>;<uri>;.
Example:

job.SearchListener = "onResults;true;POST;/servicesNS/admin/search/saved/search/foobar/notify;";

member.value:
true, if the results of the e-mail action for a
 should be created and sent as a PDF report;
otherwise, false.

true, if the scheduler should ensure that the data for a
 is automatically summarized;
otherwise, false.

true, if a realtime  managed by the
scheduler should be restarted when a new search peer becomes available;
otherwise, false.

true, if a new search should be started even if another instance
of the  is already running;
false otherwise.
